Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Bohol Regional General Hospital in the City of Tagbilaran to Governor Celestino Gallares Memorial Hospital
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 317
An Act Changing the Name of the Bohol Regional General Hospital in the City of Tagbilaran to Governor Celestino Gallares Memorial Hospital
Section 1. The name of the Bohol Regional General Hospital in the City of Tagbilaran is changed to Governor Celestino Gallares Memorial Hospital.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: November 14, 1982
